OL,3,CMan who 'inspired millions' with
OL,4,Ccandid cancer reflections dies
OL,6,FSimon was a volunteer for several
OL,7,Fother groups including the Samaritans.
OL,9,FHis selfless nature was exemplified
OL,10,Fthrough a series of candid articles
OL,11,Fthat he wrote for a local newspaper
OL,12,Ffollowing his terminal diagnosis,
OL,13,Fdetailing his treatment and
OL,14,Freflections.
OL,16,FThe pieces went viral and were read
OL,17,Fworldwide with many taking comfort
OL,18,Ffrom his words as they faced their own
OL,19,Fcancer journeys.
