OL,3,CMan who 'inspired millions' with
OL,4,Ccandid cancer reflections dies
OL,6,FSimon's tireless work to make other
OL,7,Fpeople's lives better was recognised
OL,8,Fas he was awarded the rare Silver Seal
OL,9,Fby Jersey Bailiff, Sir Timothy Le Cocq.
OL,11,FShortly before his death, Simon
OL,12,Freceived a personal letter from King
OL,13,FCharles III who praised his
OL,14,F"courageous approach" to his cancer
OL,15,Fdiagnosis and his charitable service.
OL,17,FIn his final weeks, Simon continued to
OL,18,Fattend charity board meetings and
OL,19,Fserve in the Honorary Police.
